What you need to know:

An 11-game winning run has taken City 10 points clear of the Blues at the top of the table, while third-placed Liverpool are 11 points back with a game in handIn contrast to City's formidable form, Chelsea have faltered during the busiest spell of the Premier League season, winning just one of their last five gamesWest Ham have moved back into the top four on the back of three straight wins and will be confident of extending their advantage over fifth-placed Arsenal when they host Leeds on Saturday